title.narrative: TB Data, Impact Assessment, and Communications Hub (TB DIAH)

description.narrative: The TB Data, Impact Assessment, and Communications Hub (TB DIAH) project is designed to improve the use of data for decision-making. Improved analysis of TB data will enable USAID, national TB programs (NTPs), and other key national and global stakeholders to support the planning for, and effective implementation of, TB interventions.
